is called segmented,

00:18:32.040 --> 00:18:36.840
and some tree species have an
integrated vascular structure.

00:18:36.840 --> 00:18:41.310
What that means is that some
species, the roots on this side

00:18:41.310 --> 00:18:44.670
are connected to the pipes
that run water on this side

00:18:44.670 --> 00:18:47.710
